How to configure UMS RFC
************************

   UMS RFC offers many options and this chapter explains the
configuration.  Please read it carefully because a proper configuration
is essential for the correct operation of UMS RFC.

   If you don't want to configure UMS RFC by hand you may use the
supplied Installer script. @{i}NOTE:@{ui} The Installer script only works with
with umsserver V11.32, ums.library V11.19 or better!


 @{" Environment " Link "Environment"}         AmigaDOS environment variables
 @{" UMS Configuration " Link "UMS Configuration"}   UMS configuration variables


@EndNode

