@Next "UMS Configuration"
@Toc "Configuration"

AmigaDOS environment variables
==============================

   Only one environment variable is currently used by UMS RFC:

@{b}UMSUUCP.mb@{ub}
     This variable tells the command @{"uuxqt" Link "uuxqt"} which @{"UMS message base" Link "Message Base"} it
     should use to import @{"UUCP" Link "UUCP"} batches.


