SMTP importer (server daemon)
=============================

   The command @{b}umssmtpd@{ub} is a server daemon which offers a transfer
service for mail messages via @{"SMTP" Link "SMTP"} to remote clients. It can only be
executed by the Internet Super Daemon @{"Inetd" Link "Inetd"}.

     Syntax:
     
