                      User @{b}SMTPD@{ub}
                      No password
                      Default message base

   This server offers the @{"ESMTP" Link "SMTP"} extensions SIZE, 8BITMIME and
PIPELINING. It uses the @{"UMS" Link "UMS"} configuration variable @{b}MaxMsgSize@{ub} to tell
the client what is the maximum message size which it will accept.


