Security Configuration
======================

   If you are using the commercial version of AmiTCP you may limit the
access to your system. The file @{b}AMITCP:db/inet.access@{ub} contains the
rules which services may be used on your system. The following two lines
allow the access to the services @{"NNTP" Link "NNTP"} and @{"SMTP" Link "SMTP"} from any host on the
Internet:

     smtp    *   allow   LOG
     nntp    *   allow   LOG


@EndNode

