Configuration for the Internet Super Daemon
===========================================

   The daemons for the @{"NNTP" Link "NNTP"}, @{"POP3" Link "POP3"} and @{"SMTP" Link "SMTP"} services are started
automatically when a remote host accesses those services. Add the
following three lines to the @{b}inetd@{ub} configuration file
@{b}AMITCP:db/inetd.conf@{ub}:

     smtp    stream  tcp nowait root UMS:Bin/umssmtpd umssmtpd
     pop3    stream  tcp nowait root UMS:Bin/umspop3d umspop3d
     nntp    stream  tcp nowait root UMS:Bin/umsnntpd umsnntpd


@EndNode

