Services configuration
======================

   To use the services @{"NNTP" Link "NNTP"}, @{"POP3" Link "POP3"} and @{"SMTP" Link "SMTP"} the file @{b}AMITCP:db/services@{ub}
must contain the following lines:

     smtp    25/tcp
     pop3    110/tcp
     nntp    119/tcp


